\q1
\v 9 \add But\add* now I’m mocked in their songs,
\q1 and \add my name has been made into a joke\add* by them.
\q1
\v 10 They despise me and keep their distance,
\q1 \add yet\add* don’t hesitate to spit in my face.
\q1
\v 11 \add God\add* has unstrung my bow and humbled me,
