\q1
\v 22 You hold me up to the wind and let it take me.
\q1 You toss me around in the storm.
\q1
\v 23 I know you are bringing me towards death,
\q1 and to the \add final\add* appointment that everyone has.
\q1
\v 24 Doesn’t someone who’s collapsed into a heap stretch out their hand.
